<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:11:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾敦促与中国进行无政治先决条件的对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</link><description>北京在一份政府工作报告中强化了在台湾问题上的立场后，台湾陆委会周二敦促中国接受两岸互不隶属的事实。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市因中国刺激计划不力而下跌，数据公布</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-fall-over-underwhelming-chinese-stimulus-data-tap-2024-03-05/</link><description>欧洲股市周二开盘走低，跟随亚洲股市走低，因中国在增长乏力的情况下实施经济转型的承诺未能给投资者留下深刻印象，而市场在一系列欧元区和美国经济数据公布之前变得谨慎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:16:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-fall-over-underwhelming-chinese-stimulus-data-tap-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>德国舍弗勒2023年核心利润未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-schaeffler-misses-expectations-2023-core-profit-2024-03-05/</link><description>德国汽车和工业供应商舍弗勒股份公司周二公布的全年调整后核心利润 (EBIT) 为 11.9 亿（12.9 亿美元），受到中国对该集团工业部门需求疲软的拖累。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-schaeffler-misses-expectations-2023-core-profit-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾、美国将在面向南海和台湾的岛屿举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</link><description>随着该地区与中国的紧张局势持续发酵，菲律宾和美国将于下个月在菲律宾面临南海的岛屿和台湾等关键地点举行年度军事演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>日本称中国迅速崛起的军事实力“令人严重担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-says-chinas-rapidly-rising-military-power-serious-concern-2024-03-05/</link><description>日本内阁官房长官林芳正周二表示，中国迅速扩张的军事实力令日本和国际社会“严重关切”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:26:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-says-chinas-rapidly-rising-military-power-serious-concern-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>由于财政火箭弹难以捉摸，中国投资者坚持逢低买入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</link><description>重返正在复苏的中国股市的外国投资者表示，周二宣布的支出计划不足以扭转低迷的情绪，目前继续购买股票的主要原因是它们价格便宜。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军称约翰·芬恩号航空母舰进行了从南到北台湾海峡的例行过境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-says-uss-john-finn-conducted-routine-south-to-north-taiwan-strait-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国海军周二在一份声明中表示，阿利-伯克级导弹驱逐舰约翰·芬恩号于3月5日进行了例行的南北台湾海峡过境。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:48:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-says-uss-john-finn-conducted-routine-south-to-north-taiwan-strait-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国的目标是科技自力更生；誓言向外国投资者开放制造业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-aims-self-reliance-tech-vows-open-manufacturing-foreign-investors-2024-03-05/</link><description>中国周二誓言要建设从人工智能到太空等对未来竞争力至关重要的产业，同时开放制造业和一些服务业的准入，以阻止外国投资者撤退。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-aims-self-reliance-tech-vows-open-manufacturing-foreign-investors-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商恢复英国商业地产撤退</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-developers-resume-uk-commercial-property-retreat-2024-03-05/</link><description>房地产经纪人表示，一些中国大型开发商将出售更多英国房地产以筹集现金，充分利用缓慢解冻的市场和押注复苏的买家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinese-developers-resume-uk-commercial-property-retreat-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>Cryptoverse：亚洲交易员掀起比特币热潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cryptoverse-asian-traders-give-bitcoin-blast-off-2024-03-05/</link><description>比特币的疯狂上涨是由亚洲投资者推动的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cryptoverse-asian-traders-give-bitcoin-blast-off-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国李克强誓言将为陷入低迷的房地产市场提供更多支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-li-vows-more-support-property-market-stuck-doldrums-2024-03-05/</link><description>中国总理李强周二表示，中国将采取有针对性的措施稳定房地产行业，同时为“合理”的项目提供融资，北京方面希望解决令购房者担忧的未完工房产过剩问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-li-vows-more-support-property-market-stuck-doldrums-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国复星集团正探讨出售三亚亚特兰蒂斯豪华度假村</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-fosun-explores-sale-atlantis-sanya-luxury-resort-sources-say-2024-03-05/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，复星国际正寻求出售其位于中国南方的豪华度假村亚特兰蒂斯的全部或部分，作为减少债务努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 05:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-fosun-explores-sale-atlantis-sanya-luxury-resort-sources-say-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>万科保证美元债券偿付过程“有序”，应对流动性担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-vanke-assures-repayment-dollar-bond-amid-liquidity-worries-2024-03-05/</link><description>国家支持的万科周二表示，用于偿还 3 月 11 日到期的美元票据的资金已经到位，由于人们对这家中国开发商流动性的担忧加剧，其债券面临更大的抛售压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 05:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-vanke-assures-repayment-dollar-bond-amid-liquidity-worries-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国准备在大选前就国防费用进行早期谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-united-states-prepare-early-talks-sharing-defence-costs-2024-03-05/</link><description>韩国和美国周二表示，已任命特使启动新一轮早期谈判，讨论如何分担美国驻韩部队的费用。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:06:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-united-states-prepare-early-talks-sharing-defence-costs-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾在中国威胁下增加导弹演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-increase-missile-drills-amid-china-threats-2024-03-05/</link><description>台湾国防部长邱国正周二表示，在中国加大军事压力迫使台湾接受其主权主张之际，台湾武装部队今年将增加举行导弹演习的次数。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 02:40:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-increase-missile-drills-amid-china-threats-2024-03-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>